data.description: GREAT COMMUTER LOCATION! Easy access to Northern VA and Frederick County!  This spacious, unique house in Jefferson County has it all! Upon entering, you are greeted with a bright, 2 story foyer.  A large eat in kitchen, a formal living room, large family room, dining room, laundry area and half bath complete the first floor.  Upstairs, you will find 4 large bedrooms, including a primary with ensuite bath.  Another full bath is centrally located for the other 3 bedrooms.  Outside, there is a large inground pool (new liner 2023), and a large building that could be finished to create more living space with an awning to provide shade.  The pool area is enclosed with a 6 ft vinyl privacy fence.  The large, 2 acre lot is tucked back at the end of a cul-de-sac giving the entire property privacy. Roof, gutters, and windows were replaced in 2018. MOTIVATED Seller-bring all offers
